cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.NE 

The paper deals with medical image analysis using deep neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of pre-trained classification networks and data augmentation also suggests a focus on machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of Positron Emission Tomography/Computed Tomography data also suggests a possible connection to multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the use of neural networks for segmentation is a common topic in neural networks (cs.NE).
